text: Miloš Kolejka was a gymnast from Czechoslovakia Kolejka competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics. He was born on 18 October 1926 and died on 30 October 2020.Miloš Kolejka == References == Category:1926 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Czechoslovak gymnasts Category:Olympians for Czechoslovakia
